{"tid":538684,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩電鬚刨推介","createTime":"2018-01-24T00:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T18:02:16.000Z","uid":12501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"14c1f82aa3b1e3365b243e516bf6e28cffebfb96","tid":538684,"uid":12501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:03:07.000Z","msg":"小弟之前用啲幾舊水cheap雞飛利浦，<br />\n成日剃唔乾淨又唔多夠力咁<br />\n新年想屌個貴少少既刨<br />\nBudget &lt;1500<br />\n百靈個堆有無邊個model抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c04abd3a4dc5d10c567086b62c8a43f2e4ef29","tid":538684,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:59:03.000Z","msg":"舊嗰個用左幾耐"},{"pid":"6da69634d4f2b24d46012513b7e76bda7669871b","tid":538684,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:59:52.000Z","msg":"amazon 買7系"},{"pid":"c28e997e08d980c5fccecfc17f36392eec27c33c","tid":538684,"uid":12501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c04abd3a4dc5d10c567086b62c8a43f2e4ef29","tid":538684,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:59:03.000Z","msg":"舊嗰個用左幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"2年到啦"},{"pid":"2a98e7fb261e0269705a6bbbe9362d9502585820","tid":538684,"uid":85284,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T20:44:21.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n買電鬚刨根本唔應該買貴價貨<br />\n刀片係損耗品，用用下自然就變鈍<br />\n跟住買刀片就會俾人劏<br />\n我用開 Panasonic 百幾蚊嗰啲電鬚刨<br />\n覺得性價比極高<br />\n就算用一兩年，因為刀片鈍咗而換個部新<br />\n都一啲都唔肉赤"},{"pid":"49ae1149e34b1c5c8c5090f796b90f9f7d10d6b4","tid":538684,"uid":29549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T21:08:44.000Z","msg":"我都想買過個新 求介紹"},{"pid":"d95ad584f70026529ada8fdc58eea7edfc7ba594","tid":538684,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da69634d4f2b24d460125